UPDATE talent SET bio = 'Split Signal is a project born from the creative synergy between two selectors who understand the art of the long night. Anchored by Sereda''s captivating live vocal performances, the duo weaves through jazz-inflected electronica and soulful house with an effortless cool that few can replicate. Their sets move fluidly — opening with lush, classic-leaning compositions before pulling listeners into hybrid territory where broken beats meet deep melodic textures. When the tempo rises, expect peak-time tech house delivered with raw club precision. But it''s in the early morning hours where Split Signal truly shines: stripped-back, hypnotic minimal grooves that lock the room into a collective trance. Essential listening for anyone chasing substance on the dancefloor.' WHERE alias = 'SPLIT SIGNAL';